## Usage

### Invoking Skills

#### Method 1: AI Routing (Recommended)

```
vibe route "<your request>"
```

Example:
```
vibe route "help me implement a login system"
# Output: 🤖 Matched: gstack/plan-eng-review (95%)
```

#### Method 2: Direct Invocation

```
vibe skills use <skill-id>
```

Example:
```
vibe skills use tdd
```

### Skill Information

To view skill details:
```
vibe skills info <skill-id>
```

