## Installing Skill Packs

### From Registry

```
vibe skills install gstack
vibe skills install superpowers
```

### Manual Installation

1. Clone/download skill pack
2. Place in `~/.claude/skills/`
3. Rebuild config: `vibe build claude-code`

## Creating Custom Skills

### Skill Structure

```
skills/my-skill/
├── SKILL.md          # Skill definition
└── metadata.yaml     # Optional metadata
```

### SKILL.md Format

```markdown
---
name: My Skill
description: Does something useful
trigger_when: User asks for help with X
---

# My Skill

## When to Use
- Condition 1
- Condition 2

## Steps
1. First step
2. Second step
3. Verification

## Completion Criteria
- [ ] Criterion 1
- [ ] Criterion 2
```

## Skill Registry

View all available skills:
